Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:37.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:40.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 是情書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:43.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是 這是普通的信而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:45.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大家現在不都這樣玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:46.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:47.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:51.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,待會我也給由加莉寫一封
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:53.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的好意我心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:55.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但上課的時候要認真聽課啊 美奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比起學習 還是友情比較重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最近女生之間流行寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定也有在寫情書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:09.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她們寫什麼都很認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,情書嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:15.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,直接用嘴說就好了 居然還特意寫在紙上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她們還真不嫌麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:19.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看來她們挺閒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}對不起對不起對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 早苗 你幹得太過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一下就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還是要踢一腳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,翻到課本76頁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學也在寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:56.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說到底高木同學也只是個普通的女生而已嘛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是信 誰送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼要寫給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定也有在寫情書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不不 這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定是誰的惡作劇…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:14.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這說不定是高木同學的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 肯定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:22.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,等等 要是弄錯了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要不是高木同學寫的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一旦我收到信件的事情暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:27.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定又會被高木同學捉弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天天氣不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是不是在瞞著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但感覺你好可疑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,臉還那麼紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是你的錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是錯覺就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你為什麼不翻開課本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:00.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這和你臉紅有關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:06.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有 我的臉也沒有紅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:10.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都說了什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我的錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有 夾在書裡的那封信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:22.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我放的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:27.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然是她幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種把戲 我完全看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:36.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:40.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是裝不知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不看看裡面寫了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼 裡面寫了東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,肯定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正又是捉弄我的內容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛不說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:01.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那既然你寫了 我就看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你現在看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:08.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為這節課下課之後就放學了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,想你在那之前答覆我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,答 答覆？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,需要作出回復的信件 也就是說裡面有提問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:22.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,內容難道不只是惡作劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定也有在寫情書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說有可能是情書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:37.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道是情書什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又默不出聲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我看 我會看的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看了就行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:53.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,照那麼說 裡面寫的肯定是惡作劇之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那無論裡面寫了什麼 我都要保持鎮定不被她捉弄到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,堂堂正正地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:06.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然肯定是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但要真是情書的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:14.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我該…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:23.58,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\frx8\fry0\frz352.3\move(641.6,408,643.2,308.8,195,4908)}給西片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:23.58,Takagisan-huamian,,0,0,0,,{\frz345.8\frx2\fry4\move(657.6,917.2,660.8,840.4,195,4908)\fad(200,0)}今天一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,直接跟我說不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在流行寫信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:45.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且 我也想看看你會有怎樣的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你果然是在捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:54.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吵死了 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,入學典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀 麻煩你專門跑一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:24.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:28.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,新生 你的名字叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,您問我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我叫西片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 祝賀你入學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:41.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在接下來的一年裡 你們就是一起學習的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不會要求你們每時每刻都保持融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但希望你們儘可能和諧相處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是掉到哪裡去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 剛開學也沒有什麼需要嘮叨的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,突然就來了個睡過頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.35,0:09:06.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的膽量我倒是挺佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我叫西片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,算了 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好顯眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在被定性為遲到型角色之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,得趕緊和大家打好交道 解開誤會才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,田邊老師 能打擾一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,車子好像晚點才到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,遲到了嗎 那儀式也要推遲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在入學典禮的準備時間延長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像會耽擱不少時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在這期間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:58.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們來決定座位順序
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:10.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,偏偏抽到了最後一排最角落的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,放在平時會是件令人高興的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但對現在的我來說只有壞處
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本來就一個人也不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在左邊和後面都沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:23.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且旁邊坐的還是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你真的睡過頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她向我搭話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為老師好像跟你說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:37.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,該怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是沒有遲到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我都明明準時到學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都怪一個叫高木同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 所有人去體育館
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,安靜一點 不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:11:00.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:15.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們總有一天會得到選舉權這筆無價的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:21.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最重要的是要選擇值得信賴的政治家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:25.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,請務必 讓爸爸和媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,演講太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:31.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,大叔的演講就是長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無論在小學還是中學都沒什麼變化嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過開學第一天就遲到 你也是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:42.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要吵了 回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快點坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天就到此結束了 明天開始正式上課
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:09.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要因為是開學典禮就得意忘形 要乖乖回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:17.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我來猜猜今天西片遲到的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是一次就猜中 那就算我贏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一次是猜不中的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.68,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是去送還失物了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂 你太吵了西片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:41.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:59.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,做自我介紹的時候你不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的反應是怎麼回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說 那一塊很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:14.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你幫我撿回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以後請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,換座位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:43.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,七十二 七十三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:49.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,七十四 七十五
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有點肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:12.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上好 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天要換座位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,班會課的時候換
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:10.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,班會課不是第一節嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}高木同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:39.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為 好久沒有換過座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然也有值得期待的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:55.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但我還是覺得西片旁邊的位置比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她又要捉弄我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,所有人都抽籤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:25.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 按簽上面寫的調換座位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片是多少號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,29號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 又是在最後一排呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:38.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我在中間那列的第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們離得好遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:46.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:49.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉 考試的時候告訴我答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不對 一般來說那算抄襲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是相互幫助啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:58.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈要怎麼幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我從後面給你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喲 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你坐這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 是對面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 要是在附近就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:17.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我最近視力變差了 不知道能不能看清黑板呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,旁邊坐的原來是西片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:40.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 你這反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼 不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:56.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只是不能和中井坐到一塊 有點失落而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中井的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:09.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有誰能和我換換座位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:13.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,坐著講台的正前方 我要怎麼偷吃午飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有正當理由的話 不可以換座位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有木村 你跟我來教員室一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,講台正前方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:29.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得還是西片旁邊的位置比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,木村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我視力不太好 我們交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:53.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 我已經換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:11.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把座位換到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:31.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我讓中井同學和木村同學以看不見黑板為由換了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為中井坐到了最前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:37.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原本坐他旁邊的我就和真野換了位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:41.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為真野個子小 坐前面比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:48.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片 你原本打算換到我旁邊的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:55.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個 因為我看不清黑板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,開始上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,把課本拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片想跟我說什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:17.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,從早上開始 你就一直想和我說些什麼似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:28.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這個 抱歉還晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:31.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是暑假那時的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,入學典禮那天的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:38.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片才是 虧你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我把它洗乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:55.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不過 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我是指各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比如把手帕還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又能一起坐什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個…各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,以後也請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I do not say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:17.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}在這篇文章裡 do是一般現在時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:22.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}這時把它變成過去式的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:48.16,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs55\pos(1107.6,324.4)}給高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:48.16,Takagisan-huamian-1,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs55\pos(726.4,492.4)}非常感謝
